, "haeadd1d3ga8a6g48f9g8eb2gbd2a5193cc7b": ["Ettercaps, no doubt. Spiders aren't so wasteful.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Campsite_PAD.html", "bbb2cb67-0f37-9ffc-01b1-aeedd0039823"], "h4b2e9470gec64g474bg9788gb7705a295324": ["This is the work of ettercaps - stalkers by nature. They could already be hunting us...", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Campsite_PAD.html", "bbb2cb67-0f37-9ffc-01b1-aeedd0039823"], "h4ce829eagffbdg4b18g9132g88364e289f41": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Campsite_PAD.html", "bbb2cb67-0f37-9ffc-01b1-aeedd0039823"], "h20969915g1e4cg4befg91a0gf089f4ffb345": ["|Karla comment!|", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Campsite_PAD.html", "bbb2cb67-0f37-9ffc-01b1-aeedd0039823"], "hdfcd25c9g3063g4728gbad6g72762fdbbdb8": ["Ettercaps. The twin claw-trails in the blood leave no doubt.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Campsite_PAD.html", "bbb2cb67-0f37-9ffc-01b1-aeedd0039823"], "h7fe866a7gd135g49c6gae2ag1de5384f1da2": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Campsite_PAD.html", "bbb2cb67-0f37-9ffc-01b1-aeedd0039823"], "hffdc4792g5d61g4a7eg98f8gbfdbce3b4f7c": ["Ettercaps. They certainly made a mess here...", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Campsite_PAD.html", "bbb2cb67-0f37-9ffc-01b1-aeedd0039823"], "h79b8ec24g3aceg4003g81b5g5d9fed0e5302": ["I've seen this sort of thing. Ettercaps, sure as sunshine.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Campsite_PAD.html", "bbb2cb67-0f37-9ffc-01b1-aeedd0039823"], "h33dfbe6bgd36dg4461gba2bgc6662a608ce9": ["No ordinary spiders did this. Ettercaps ripped the place to pieces.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Campsite_PAD.html", "bbb2cb67-0f37-9ff